{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"handleOpenURL:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handleOpenURL:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"url"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The URL to process."}]}],"name":"url"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"YES if the URL was handled by Pushwoosh, NO otherwise.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handles special Pushwoosh URLs, primarily used for:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Test device registration"}]},{"text":": Register device for push testing via QR code","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Deep link tracking","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Process tracked deep links from push notifications"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Should be called from your app’s URL handling methods. Returns YES if the URL","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"was a Pushwoosh URL and was handled, NO if it should be processed by your app."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","type":"heading","text":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle URLs in SceneDelegate (iOS 13+):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class SceneDelegate: UIResponder, UIWindowSceneDelegate {","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, openURLContexts URLContexts: Set<UIOpenURLContext>) {","        guard let url = URLContexts.first?.url else { return }","","        \/\/ First, check if Pushwoosh handles this URL","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            Logger.info(\"URL handled by Pushwoosh\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Handle other deep links","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, continue userActivity: NSUserActivity) {","        guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","              let url = userActivity.webpageURL else { return }","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return","        }","","        UniversalLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}","","\/\/ Legacy AppDelegate support","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ app: UIApplication,","                    open url: URL,","                    options: [UIApplication.OpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return true","        }","","        return DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handleOpenURL:":{"kind":"symbol","title":"handleOpenURL:","abstract":[{"text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"}}}